OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780589464
OL,3,CBlue badge parking scheme being abused
OL,4,Cat 'surprising level', says council
OL,6,FThe blue badge parking scheme is being
OL,7,Fabused in what enforcement teams
OL,8,Fdescribe as a "surprising level" in
OL,9,Fparts of Sussex.
OL,11,FMid Sussex Council is stepping up
OL,12,Fefforts to crackdown on offenders,
OL,13,Fsaying people have been altering
OL,14,Fexpiry dates with pens or using a a
OL,15,Fbadge belonging to someone who has
OL,16,Fdied.
OL,18,FThe authority has seized more than 30
OL,19,Fbadges which were being misused, since
OL,20,Fadvanced training in January.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
