PN,41902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780589464
OL,3,CBlue badge parking scheme being abused
OL,4,Cat 'surprising level', says council
OL,6,FCivil enforcement officer Tristan
OL,7,FMitchell said: "I thought they'd find
OL,8,Fthe odd one or two, but 30 from the
OL,9,Fstart of the training, start of the
OL,10,Fyear, until now is a crazy high number
OL,11,Fto be finding out there on the streets
OL,12,Fand in the car parks.
OL,14,FHe added that by using a device,
OL,15,Fofficers can root out the illegal use
OL,16,Fof blue badges in just seconds, by
OL,17,Fchecking things like the badge
OL,18,Fholder's name, photo and address.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780589464
OL,3,CBlue badge parking scheme being abused
OL,4,Cat 'surprising level', says council
OL,6,FThey can also phone badge holders to
OL,7,Fmake sure they are in the area where
OL,8,Fthe car has been parked.
OL,10,FTristan says there have been times
OL,11,Fwhen they've phoned the number
OL,12,Fattached to a blue badge, and the
OL,13,Fperson has been at home.
OL,15,FThe blue badge scheme is designed to
OL,16,Fgive freedom to people with
OL,17,Fdisabilities. The current one was
OL,18,Fintroduced in 2000 and gives people
OL,19,Fwith disabilities closer parking to
OL,20,Ffacilities like shops and surgeries.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780589464
OL,3,CBlue badge parking scheme being abused
OL,4,Cat 'surprising level', says council
OL,6,FUsers in Haywards Heath have praised
OL,7,Fthe council's crackdown and are
OL,8,Fappalled at those taking advantage.
OL,10,FOne said: "It makes me feel furious.
OL,11,FIf I don't have access to a car park
OL,12,Fspace I can't come to the shops.
OL,13,FPeople are criminal in the fact that
OL,14,Fthey misuse blue badges.
OL,16,FMeanwhile, another couple told us:
OL,17,F"It's appalling. Really bad because
OL,18,Fother people, you know, that need it,
OL,19,Fand the space is gone."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780589464
OL,3,CBlue badge parking scheme being abused
OL,4,Cat 'surprising level', says council
OL,6,FAcross the country it's thought there
OL,7,Fare 3 million blue badges in
OL,8,Fcirculation - but as many as 1 in 5,
OL,9,Fequating to 600,000, are being used
OL,10,Fincorrectly, and fakes are being sold
OL,11,Fon social media.
OL,13,FCivil enforcement officer Tristan
OL,14,Fadded that people have been using
OL,15,Ftactics like changing expiry dates
OL,16,Fwith pens or using a a badge belonging
OL,17,Fto someone who has died for "a number
OL,18,Fof years" before officers finally
OL,19,Fcaught them in the act.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780589464
OL,3,CBlue badge parking scheme being abused
OL,4,Cat 'surprising level', says council
OL,6,FMisusing a blue badge is a criminal
OL,7,Foffence and can result in a fine of up
OL,8,Fto #1,000.
OL,10,FBut Mid Sussex Council said it doesn't
OL,11,Fwant to go down that route at first.
OL,12,FInstead, it hopes it can educate and
OL,13,Fmake people aware of how to use the
OL,14,Fscheme legitimately.
OL,16,FSimon Hughes, Director of People and
OL,17,FCommercial Services for Mid Sussex
OL,18,FCouncil said it is "immensely"
OL,19,Fdisappointing that people are
OL,20,Fknowingly misusing the blue badge
OL,21,Fscheme.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780589464
OL,3,CBlue badge parking scheme being abused
OL,4,Cat 'surprising level', says council
OL,6,F"The people that use them illegally,
OL,7,Fthey know what they're doing. And that
OL,8,Fhas an impact, a real impact on
OL,9,Fvulnerable people.
OL,11,F"And not all those people are visibly
OL,12,Fvulnerable, so some of them could have
OL,13,Fspecial educational needs.
OL,15,F"Some of them could have disabilities
OL,16,Fthat you wouldn't immediately notice,
OL,17,Fbut absolutely have to be close to
OL,18,Fwhere they can use those services.
OL,20,F"So it has a significant impact on
OL,21,Fpeople."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
