OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780589464
OL,3,CBlue badge parking scheme being abused
OL,4,Cat 'surprising level', says council
OL,6,FHe added that he also works with
OL,7,Fchildren who have special educational
OL,8,Fneeds, so being very close to
OL,9,Fsomewhere they can go to matters for
OL,10,Ftheir personal safety.
OL,12,F"It means they can get out the house,
OL,13,Fit means they can do the activities
OL,14,Fthat all children choose to do - but
OL,15,Fthey can't if they cant get a space
OL,16,Fclose to those facilities."
OL,18,FAnd for those abusing the system, the
OL,19,Fcouncil is warning that "time is up".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
